"Change Set:		9319Collections-ar.303Collections-ar.303:Change EncodedCharSet>>digitValue: to EncodedCharSet>>digitValueOf:. Part 2/3.Collections-dtl.302:Eliminate explicit Transcripter dependency on MVC Paragraph. Note that Transcripter currently lacks a Morphic view."!!Transcripter methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'dtl 2/10/2010 22:15'!initInFrame: rect	frame := rect insetBy: 2.  "Leave room for border"	(Smalltalk hasClassNamed: #Paragraph)		ifFalse: [^ self inform: 'MVC class Paragraph not present'].	para := (Smalltalk at: #Paragraph) withText: self contents asText				style: TextStyle default				compositionRectangle: ((frame insetBy: 4) withHeight: 9999)				clippingRectangle: frame				foreColor: self black backColor: self white! !!Character methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'ar 2/11/2010 23:38'!digitValue	"Answer 0-9 if the receiver is $0-$9, 10-35 if it is $A-$Z, and < 0 	otherwise. This is used to parse literal numbers of radix 2-36."	| digitValue |	(digitValue := ('0123456789ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ' indexOf: self) - 1) >= 0		ifTrue: [ ^digitValue ].	^ (EncodedCharSet charsetAt: self leadingChar) digitValueOf: self.! !